WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.500
The void opens like a forgotten breath behind my eyes.

00:00:06.200 --> 00:00:10.617
No horizon, only the slow bloom of invisible thunder.

00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:17.867
I dissolve into black silk, weightless and unremembered.

00:00:20.600 --> 00:00:25.433
Somewhere, silence is building a cathedral out of absence.

